parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description:
The client token that is used to ensure the idempotence of the request. You can use the client to generate the token, but you must make sure that the token is unique among different requests.

The token can contain only ASCII characters and cannot exceed 64 characters in length.

parameters.name: KmsResourceId
parameters.description: The ID of the KMS resource. Only key IDs are supported.

parameters.name: KmsResourceRegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the region to which the KMS resource belongs.

parameters.name: KmsResourceType
parameters.description: The type of the KMS resource. Only key is supported.

parameters.name: KmsResourceUser
parameters.description: The ID of the Alibaba Cloud account to which the KMS resource belongs.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID. You can call the DescribeRegions operation to query the most recent region list.
